ZH: 他喜欢骑自行车去上班。
EN: He likes to ride his bike to work.

ZH: 我们可以骑马去山上。
EN: We can ride horses up the mountain.

ZH: 她学会了如何骑滑板。
EN: She learned how to ride a skateboard.

ZH: 他们昨天去海边骑了摩托车。
EN: They rode motorcycles to the beach yesterday.

ZH: 孩子们喜欢骑旋转木马。
EN: The children enjoy riding on the carousel.

ZH: 你会骑电动车吗？
EN: Can you ride an electric scooter?

ZH: 明天我们计划去公园骑单车。
EN: We plan to go to the park and ride bikes tomorrow.

ZH: 我们应该小心骑自行车上陡坡。
EN: We should be careful riding bikes down steep hills.

ZH: 他喜欢在农田里骑马。
EN: He enjoys riding horses in the countryside.

ZH: 我骑车走错了路。
EN: I got lost while riding my bike.

ZH: 她让我骑在她的电动摩托车上。
EN: She let me ride on her electric scooter.

ZH: 昨天我骑了一个小时的摩托车。
EN: I rode a motorcycle for an hour yesterday.

ZH: 小猫喜欢骑在主人的肩膀上。
EN: The kitten likes to ride on its owner's shoulder.

ZH: 他骑着自行车去了足球场。
EN: He rode his bike to the soccer field.

ZH: 我怕骑巴士。
EN: I'm afraid of riding the bus.

ZH: 明年我想跨国骑自行车。
EN: I want to ride my bike across countries next year.

ZH: 他们决定骑马度过周末。
EN: They decided to spend the weekend riding horses.

ZH: 你可以骑在我的背上。
EN: You can ride on my back.

ZH: 她喜欢找时间骑着自行车四周转。
EN: She enjoys finding time to ride her bike around.

ZH: 她很勇敢，敢给别人骑马。
EN: She's very brave to allow others to ride her horse.
